  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b95\u0bb2 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b92\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Enough of being divided, all political parties should work together - President Ranil",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is necessary to work with a new policy to solve the crisis situation that the country is facing. Despite being divided, I call upon all political parties to work together.",
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe told the House that he is ready to engage in negotiations with all parties from today regarding working together.",
        "My life is in Parliament. A high honor has been conferred through Parliament. President Ranil Wickremesinghe urged the Speaker to grant permission to take the oath of office as President in the Parliament building.",
        "The President mentioned the above in a special address following the official announcement by the Parliamentary Secretary General to the House that Ranil Wickremesinghe has been elected as the President following the completion of the presidential poll.",
        "Speaker (awakening the Speaker) You and I started our political journey in 1973.",
        "I have been involved in parliamentary politics for 45 years. My life is in Parliament. So I express my special thanks for conferring this honor on me through Parliament.",
        "Following the assassination of the then President Ranasinghe Premadasa in 1993, Parliament convened to elect a new President.",
        "DP Vijayatunga was elected unopposed. 15 of those who participated in the presidential election that day are still members of Parliament.",
        "Election of the President through the Parliament took place for the first time with a referendum. Through various negotiations, the presidential poll was held without any contradictions to the parliamentary democracy.",
        "There is no need to mention anything new about the crisis situation the country is facing. Young people expect a new political culture. We need to move forward without getting caught up in global issues.",
        "People expect a new political process. I would like to thank Dallas Alagaperuma and Anura Kumara Dissanayake who competed with me.",
        "Let's work together with a new plan. My friend Anura Kumara Dissanayake and my friend Dalus should also work together with us.",
        "Similarly, I call upon Sambandhan and GG Ponnambalam, CV Wickhineswaran, former President Mahinda Rajapaksa and former President Maithripala Sirisena of the Tamil National Federation to work together.",
        "Ready to engage in talks with everyone from today about working together when divided.",
        "He said that he would request permission to take the oath of office as President in the Parliament building."
      ],
